{"tid":1924153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［英國手足請入］應承我，有事都唔好搵中國大使","createTime":"2020-03-13T13:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T03:29:46.000Z","uid":229185,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"de70eeb367934b158a43c895d1069d9e57992a90","tid":1924153,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎全球大流行，英國疫情亦趨失控，有在當地修讀音樂的香港學生懷疑中招，個多星期前出現懷疑病徵，但當地卻沒有醫院及診所收治，只稱會郵寄新冠病毒測試劑給他，惟一星期過去他並沒收到試劑，身體狀況卻漸差，由普通感冒病徵至現時暈眩及肚瀉。其母在港求助議員葛珮帆，葛向入境處反映、望尋求中國駐英國大使館介入。葛正等候進一步消息，又擔心大量學生在英國及歐洲留學，事件或是冰山一角。<br />\n葛珮帆表示，港生母親日前求助，指兒子在倫敦留學、並與女朋友同住。一個多星期前，事主出現新冠肺炎的病徵，懷疑中招，由於英國當局只會為與確診患者親密接觸過的人士進行病毒測試，港生只能在家中自我隔離，其後，事主女友的老師確診患上新冠肺炎，其女友亦開始出現相關病徵。<br />\n港生患病後，曾致電私家診所求助，因涉及新冠肺炎遭拒絕應診，他致電當地專線尋求協助。開始獲告知48小時回覆，並會郵寄測試劑給他，港生可將試劑樣本寄回負責部門進行病毒測試。但一星期後仍未獲回覆，致電求助時又無法接通。<br />\n葛珮帆表示，立即聯絡港府相關部門，入境處已經與在倫敦的事主及其母親聯絡，並在<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">事主同意下要求中國駐英國大使館提供協助</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200313/mobile/bkn-20200313131949022-0313_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200313%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200313131949022-0313_00822_001.html&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7jwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=b3949eed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200313/mobile/bkn-20200313131949022-0313_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有其他英國手足跪低左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係有比啲藍屍有位入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578b23e5997e860b3f73922ff4968b272b641dd8","tid":1924153,"uid":229185,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我哋要堅持呀"},{"pid":"73304553beee92d5ee331f0f7509bb461bad21ae","tid":1924153,"uid":126382,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:38:23.000Z","msg":"冇bno咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"886bf72243bbf1df473dea3fd9585cacc3d68bf6","tid":1924153,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73304553beee92d5ee331f0f7509bb461bad21ae","tid":1924153,"uid":126382,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:38:23.000Z","msg":"冇bno咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:39:05.000Z","msg":"肯定係特衰中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n趕佢返中國香港就啱"},{"pid":"25168ac7a1b31673d7c3bb72c3dccdd8111a03ed","tid":1924153,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:40:16.000Z","msg":"仲係學生點會有啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd9f13c55e229d84be6f19b2d02d30c031cb6ad","tid":1924153,"uid":229185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73304553beee92d5ee331f0f7509bb461bad21ae","tid":1924153,"uid":126382,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:38:23.000Z","msg":"冇bno咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:40:50.000Z","msg":"新一代好似冇"},{"pid":"06c251953a65d8e3153ddcea19c4eda4b07329b5","tid":1924153,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:41:53.000Z","msg":"寧死不屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgm